If your return package is scanned "accepted" on the USPS tracking within ten days of the date the jewelry was delivered to you, you will receive a one hundred percent refund without a restock fee.  (Example:  Jewelry marked "delivered" to you on the 1st of the month must be marked "accepted" by the post office on or before the 11th to qualify for restock fee waiver.)

Jewelry must be brand new, unworn and unaltered, with tags still attached.

Title: 18k Gold Plated Fancy Beads 10" Anklet Made in Italy 3x Thicker Gold Fancy-Dancy
Description: This beautiful anklet is so fun. It is wide and thick (1/4") (7mm) and very showy. The beads move a little to give this anklet a kinetic quality. The anklet is high polished, and the connecting bars are cut at varying angles for a lot of glimmer. It closes securely with a big lobster claw clasp. This is very fine quality gold plated jewelry made in Italy. There is 75 mils of gold on this anklet. Most other gold plated jewelry on the market averages only 5 mils to 25 mils. The gold stays on this jewelry. It retains its beautiful color. We have carried this manufacturer's line of jewelry in our shop since 2007, and our customers love it. This is a wonderful look at a wonderful price and free shipping for eBay shoppers. Compare at retail $79.99+ sales tax. Thank you for looking at our listing.
